Solution
I created a directory named "tmp" using the mkdir command.
I navigated into the tmp directory using the cd command and created a file called xfusioncorp.sh using the touch commands
I used la -la command to verify that the xfusioncorp.sh file was successfully created
I used sudo chmod 555 command to give read and execute permissions to owner, group and others.
I used la -la command again to verify the permission for the xfusioncorp.sh file
I did ctrl + s to save
I did git add Day4
I ran git status to see the staged files
I ran git commit -m "uploaded Day4 file"
I then pushed to my github account.
